<item>
            <title>[LU-3736] Test failure on test suite sanity-hsm, subtest test_23</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3736</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for girish &amp;lt;gshilamkar@ddn.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/7fd98906-0154-11e3-b06c-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/7fd98906-0154-11e3-b06c-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_23 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Cannot send HSM request (use of /mnt/lustre/d0.sanity-hsm/d23/test_mtime): Device or resource busy&lt;br/&gt;
 sanity-hsm test_23: @@@@@@ FAIL: could not release file &lt;br/&gt;
  Trace dump:&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh:4202:error_noexit()&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh:4229:error()&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/sanity-hsm.sh:73:fail()&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/sanity-hsm.sh:410:test_23()&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh:4483:run_one()&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh:4516:run_one_logged()&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh:4371:run_test()&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/sanity-hsm.sh:420:main()&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Looks like this bug and &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3735&quot; title=&quot;Test failure on test suite sanity-hsm, subtest test_22&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3735&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3735&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; are symptoms of same cause.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
